“Meta”
means, as applicable, Meta Platforms, Inc. (formerly Facebook, Inc.), Meta Platforms Ireland Limited (formerly Facebook Ireland Limited), or any Affiliate of Meta Platforms, Inc. to the extent such Affiliate Processes Personal Data under the Agreement.
